Package util

Interface FilePath

All Known Implementing Classes:
AccountController, BTOSystem, EnquiryDatabase, OfficerApplicationDatabase, ProjectApplicationDatabase, ProjectDatabase, UserDatabase
public interface FilePath
Interface containing constants for file paths used in the BTO system. These file paths are used to access and store data for various system components.
